flowchart TD
    Start([Code changes committed]) --> ChooseEnv{Deployment<br/>Environment?}

    %% Minikube Local Development Path
    ChooseEnv -->|Minikube Local| MinikubeStart[Local Development Deploy]

    MinikubeStart --> MinikubeCluster{Minikube<br/>running?}
    MinikubeCluster -->|No| StartMinikube[minikube start -p tesslate<br/>--driver=docker<br/>--memory=4096 --cpus=2]
    MinikubeCluster -->|Yes| ChooseImage

    StartMinikube --> EnableIngress[minikube addons enable ingress]
    EnableIngress --> ChooseImage

    ChooseImage{Which image<br/>to build?}

    ChooseImage -->|Backend| MinikubeBackend[Build Backend Image]
    ChooseImage -->|Frontend| MinikubeFrontend[Build Frontend Image]
    ChooseImage -->|DevServer| MinikubeDevServer[Build DevServer Image]

    MinikubeBackend --> DeleteOldBackend[Delete old image:<br/>minikube ssh -- docker rmi -f<br/>tesslate-backend:latest]
    DeleteOldBackend --> DeleteLocalBackend[Delete local image:<br/>docker rmi -f<br/>tesslate-backend:latest]
    DeleteLocalBackend --> BuildBackendNoCache[Build with --no-cache:<br/>docker build --no-cache<br/>-t tesslate-backend:latest<br/>-f orchestrator/Dockerfile]

    MinikubeFrontend --> DeleteOldFrontend[Delete old image:<br/>minikube ssh -- docker rmi -f<br/>tesslate-frontend:latest]
    DeleteOldFrontend --> DeleteLocalFrontend[Delete local image:<br/>docker rmi -f<br/>tesslate-frontend:latest]
    DeleteLocalFrontend --> BuildFrontendNoCache[Build with --no-cache:<br/>docker build --no-cache<br/>-t tesslate-frontend:latest<br/>-f app/Dockerfile.prod]

    MinikubeDevServer --> DeleteOldDevServer[Delete old image:<br/>minikube ssh -- docker rmi -f<br/>tesslate-devserver:latest]
    DeleteOldDevServer --> DeleteLocalDevServer[Delete local image:<br/>docker rmi -f<br/>tesslate-devserver:latest]
    DeleteLocalDevServer --> BuildDevServerNoCache[Build with --no-cache:<br/>docker build --no-cache<br/>-t tesslate-devserver:latest<br/>-f orchestrator/Dockerfile.devserver]

    BuildBackendNoCache --> LoadBackend[Load to Minikube:<br/>minikube image load<br/>tesslate-backend:latest]
    BuildFrontendNoCache --> LoadFrontend[Load to Minikube:<br/>minikube image load<br/>tesslate-frontend:latest]
    BuildDevServerNoCache --> LoadDevServer[Load to Minikube:<br/>minikube image load<br/>tesslate-devserver:latest]

    LoadBackend --> DeleteBackendPod[Force pod restart:<br/>kubectl delete pod -n tesslate<br/>-l app=tesslate-backend]
    LoadFrontend --> DeleteFrontendPod[Force pod restart:<br/>kubectl delete pod -n tesslate<br/>-l app=tesslate-frontend]
    LoadDevServer --> MinikubeComplete[DevServer image ready<br/>for user containers]

    DeleteBackendPod --> WaitBackend[Wait for rollout:<br/>kubectl rollout status<br/>deployment/tesslate-backend]
    DeleteFrontendPod --> WaitFrontend[Wait for rollout:<br/>kubectl rollout status<br/>deployment/tesslate-frontend]

    WaitBackend --> VerifyBackend[Verify deployment:<br/>kubectl exec -- grep 'code'<br/>in deployed files]
    WaitFrontend --> VerifyFrontend[Verify deployment:<br/>kubectl exec -- ls -la /usr/share/nginx/html/assets/]

    VerifyBackend --> MinikubeComplete
    VerifyFrontend --> MinikubeComplete
    MinikubeComplete --> AccessMinikube[Access via:<br/>- minikube tunnel<br/>- kubectl port-forward]

    AccessMinikube --> TestLocal[Test on localhost]
    TestLocal --> DeployEnd([Deploy Complete])

    %% AWS EKS Production Path
    ChooseEnv -->|AWS EKS Prod| EKSStart[Production Deploy]

    EKSStart --> ConfigureAWS[Configure AWS CLI:<br/>Use tesslate-terraform credentials]
    ConfigureAWS --> UpdateKubeconfig[Update kubeconfig:<br/>aws eks update-kubeconfig<br/>--region us-east-1<br/>--name tesslate-cluster]

    UpdateKubeconfig --> LoginECR[Login to ECR:<br/>aws ecr get-login-password<br/>| docker login]

    LoginECR --> ChooseEKSImage{Which image<br/>to deploy?}

    ChooseEKSImage -->|Backend| EKSBackend[Backend Pipeline]
    ChooseEKSImage -->|Frontend| EKSFrontend[Frontend Pipeline]
    ChooseEKSImage -->|DevServer| EKSDevServer[DevServer Pipeline]
    ChooseEKSImage -->|All| EKSAll[All Images Pipeline]

    EKSBackend --> BuildEKSBackend[docker build --no-cache<br/>-t tesslate-backend:latest<br/>-f orchestrator/Dockerfile]
    BuildEKSBackend --> TagEKSBackend[docker tag tesslate-backend:latest<br/>AWS_ACCOUNT.dkr.ecr.us-east-1<br/>.amazonaws.com/tesslate-backend:latest]
    TagEKSBackend --> PushEKSBackend[docker push AWS_ACCOUNT.dkr.ecr<br/>.us-east-1.amazonaws.com<br/>/tesslate-backend:latest]

    EKSFrontend --> BuildEKSFrontend[docker build --no-cache<br/>-t tesslate-frontend:latest<br/>-f app/Dockerfile.prod]
    BuildEKSFrontend --> TagEKSFrontend[docker tag tesslate-frontend:latest<br/>AWS_ACCOUNT.dkr.ecr.us-east-1<br/>.amazonaws.com/tesslate-frontend:latest]
    TagEKSFrontend --> PushEKSFrontend[docker push AWS_ACCOUNT.dkr.ecr<br/>.us-east-1.amazonaws.com<br/>/tesslate-frontend:latest]

    EKSDevServer --> BuildEKSDevServer[docker build --no-cache<br/>-t tesslate-devserver:latest<br/>-f orchestrator/Dockerfile.devserver]
    BuildEKSDevServer --> TagEKSDevServer[docker tag tesslate-devserver:latest<br/>AWS_ACCOUNT.dkr.ecr.us-east-1<br/>.amazonaws.com/tesslate-devserver:latest]
    TagEKSDevServer --> PushEKSDevServer[docker push AWS_ACCOUNT.dkr.ecr<br/>.us-east-1.amazonaws.com<br/>/tesslate-devserver:latest]

    EKSAll --> BuildEKSBackend
    EKSAll --> BuildEKSFrontend
    EKSAll --> BuildEKSDevServer

    PushEKSBackend --> DeleteBackendPodEKS[Force pull new image:<br/>kubectl delete pod -n tesslate<br/>-l app=tesslate-backend]
    PushEKSFrontend --> DeleteFrontendPodEKS[Force pull new image:<br/>kubectl delete pod -n tesslate<br/>-l app=tesslate-frontend]
    PushEKSDevServer --> EKSDevServerReady[DevServer ready<br/>for user containers]

    DeleteBackendPodEKS --> WaitBackendEKS[Wait for pod ready:<br/>kubectl get pods -n tesslate]
    DeleteFrontendPodEKS --> WaitFrontendEKS[Wait for pod ready:<br/>kubectl get pods -n tesslate]

    WaitBackendEKS --> RestartIngress[Restart NGINX Ingress:<br/>kubectl rollout restart<br/>deployment/ingress-nginx-controller<br/>-n ingress-nginx]
    WaitFrontendEKS --> RestartIngress

    RestartIngress --> WaitIngressReady[Wait for Ingress ready:<br/>kubectl rollout status<br/>-n ingress-nginx]

    WaitIngressReady --> VerifyEKS[Verify deployment:<br/>kubectl exec -- check files]

    VerifyEKS --> CheckCerts{SSL certs<br/>valid?}

    CheckCerts -->|No| CheckCertManager[Check cert-manager logs:<br/>kubectl logs -n cert-manager<br/>deployment/cert-manager]
    CheckCertManager --> FixCerts[Fix Cloudflare API token<br/>or DNS configuration]
    FixCerts --> CheckCerts

    CheckCerts -->|Yes| EKSComplete[Production Deploy Complete]
    EKSDevServerReady --> EKSComplete

    EKSComplete --> AccessEKS[Access via:<br/>https://saipriya.org<br/>https://api.saipriya.org]

    AccessEKS --> TestProd[Test production site]
    TestProd --> MonitorLogs[Monitor logs:<br/>kubectl logs -f deployment/tesslate-backend]

    MonitorLogs --> DeployEnd

    %% Image Pull Policy Notes
    Note1[Note: Image Pull Policies<br/>Minikube: imagePullPolicy: Never<br/>AWS EKS: imagePullPolicy: Always]
    Note2[Note: --no-cache is REQUIRED<br/>to ensure code changes are included.<br/>Docker layer caching can prevent<br/>updated code from being copied.]
    Note3[Note: Deleting pods forces K8s<br/>to pull fresh images from registry.<br/>rollout restart may use cached images.]

    MinikubeStart -.->|Reference| Note1
    EKSStart -.->|Reference| Note1
    BuildBackendNoCache -.->|Critical| Note2
    BuildEKSBackend -.->|Critical| Note2
    DeleteBackendPod -.->|Why?| Note3
    DeleteBackendPodEKS -.->|Why?| Note3

